articles.author: ELLEN KNICKMEYER | Associated Press
articles.title: Allies make the case for NATO in terms that would appeal to Trump - WKRC TV Cincinnati
articles.description: European allies in NATO are stepping up their military spending, just as Donald Trump wanted. They're pointing to common interests, such as concerns over China.
